{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_04_01",
  "title": "鈴村優 1話 うち話早い人好きよ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "この喫茶店、落ち着くやろ？\n駅前の割に空いてるし、穴場なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn't this cafe quiet?\nIt's in front of the station‚ but there aren't many people‚ it's perfect.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.5165578047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "京都に帰った時は、よく寄るんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I often stop by when I go to Kyoto",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、そうなのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、なんか疲れてはるなぁ\nどうしたんです？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ you looks tired.\nWhat's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "すまない、今回の仕事は急に決まって\n直前までバタバタしていたから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ this schedule was decided in a sudden.\nI was flabbergasted until the last minute. ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "新幹線に危うく乗り遅れるところやったもんな～\nでもまぁ、間に合ったから良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ you right‚ we almost missed the Shinkansen!\nBut‚ well‚ I'm glad we made it in time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、仕事で京都来るんは\n星見プロに来てから初めてやわ。今から楽しみやなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But still‚ this is the first time for me to come to Kyoto for work\nsince I came to Hoshimi Productions. I'm looking forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.3456484992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.761769104
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "やっと生まれ故郷の仕事が出来て嬉しいわ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm so happy to finally be able to work in my hometown!~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.761769104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.661769104
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "さすが{user}さん\nうちのことよう分かってくれてはるなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's what I'm talking about‚ {user}-san.\nYou know me so well‚ don't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5951024373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ分かるよ。だって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I do know it so well‚ because…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.9951024373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 57.361769104
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "この雑誌に載ってる琴乃ちゃん\nめっちゃ可愛いなぁ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan in this magazine‚\nis just so cute~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.5951024373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "……ウエディングドレスなんか着るんやもんなぁ～\nうんうん、素敵やねぇ。やっぱよう似合うわ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……I can't believe she's going to wear a wedding dress!\nOh‚ yeah‚ it's so nice. It really looks good on her~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.3951024373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、それ、凄い反響だったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ that got a great response.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.661769104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅん、そうなんや\nうちも着てみたかったなぁ、花嫁衣装……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ I see.\nI wish I could have worn that wedding outfits too…….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.361769104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "え？　これは、黒が良く映えるデザインだから\n黒髪の子がいいって、クライアントから要望が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?　This is a design that looks good in black.\nThe client requested a girl with black hair. ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.161769104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "どんなクライアントさんなん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What kind of client?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.6284357707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "な、仲のいい星見市の企業だけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ it's a company in Hoshimi City that I'm close with…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.7951024373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "ほうほう\n地元の会社さんと仲良くされてるんやね、ええことです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ok~ Ok~ I see~\nI see you're on good terms with the local company‚ that's great.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.6951024373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、星見プロのアイドルの地元は\n今や星見市だけやないんやけどなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I think the hometown of Hoshimi Pro's idols‚\nis not only Hoshimi city now……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.061769104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃんは山形、うちは京都……\n他の子のことも、たまには思い出してほしいなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire is in Yamagata and Mine Kyoto……\nI hope you remember other idols sometimes too……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.2951024373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いや、その、今までの仕事の付き合いもあるし\n星見市や東京なら移動時間もかからないだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I mean‚ the company and I been working together for a while already.\nAnd Hoshimi City and Tokyo wouldn't take too long to travel‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.0284357707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "新幹線やったら、京都もあっという間やん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we took the Shinkansen‚ Kyoto would be just a short ride‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.8284357707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まあ、うん、そうかもしれないね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ well‚ yes‚ that's right……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.8951024373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "東京と星見市の他にも……例えば京都にも\nきっとええお仕事、あると思うんやけどなぁ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides Tokyo and Hoshimi…For example Kyoto‚\nI'm sure there are great jobs‚ too‚ tho~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.461769104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-yu017.m4a",
      "text": "うちも、京都でお仕事してみたい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'd like to work in Kyoto~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.8284357707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-yu018.m4a",
      "text": "……ああ、でも、そんなわがまま言うたらあかん\nきっと{user}さんを困らせてまう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……Ah‚ah‚ nah. I shouldn't be so selfish!\nI'm making {user}-san in trouble!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.661769104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "お口チャックやわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I must just shut my mouth up!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.961769104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "え、えーと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ eh…I mean…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.2284357707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_04_01-yu020.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、うちの独り言やから\n気にせんといて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry sorry~ I'm just talking to myself.\nDon't mind it.",
